{"tid":200934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來巴打講肥婆偷食肉呢句野係岩架！","createTime":"2017-04-14T11:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T07:22:28.000Z","uid":133,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e401d2dc2ec2333994cdb6423fa7f331c96860","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"話說今日同女朋友去食麥當勞，叫咗個18件麥樂雞餐同埋東京之夜嘅套餐，正打算坐低等人送餐之際。<br />\n<br />\n隔離枱坐左個肥婆，個麥當勞妹妹仔放低左一個同我地個餐一模一樣嘅餐比嗰個肥婆，初時我都有懷疑過果餐應該係我哋嘅，但係我女朋友話可能佢等緊朋友或者佢真係食兩個餐呢。<br />\n<br />\n我見佢面容有啲戚戚然咁嘅微笑，然後一個箭步拎埋個餐出咗櫃檯，咁我梗係跟埋出去，問吓個職員係咪比錯左餐，當我行到埋櫃檯嘅時候，個職員竟然幫個肥婆將個堂食變做外賣，我就問嗰個肥婆：「個餐會唔會係我哋架，冇理由同我地嗰個一樣架，我哋等左好耐。」個肥婆扮晒傻，一句野都冇講過。咁我以為佢check咗但應該冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n重點就嚟啦，之後有個阿叔攞住個巨無霸餐走出嚟派餐，正當佢想放低係我張枱嘅時候，我就話我叫嗰個餐唔叫係巨無霸餐喎。嗰陣時我就知賴嘢，一定係個肥婆偷食肉，而且佢已經逃脫左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就揸住我自己張單，走出去櫃檯，同個職員講我個餐等咗好耐都未黎，幫佢檢查完嗰個單之後，佢就叫入面整多個18件麥樂雞俾我，當後邊嗰個阿姐聽到嘅時候，都話：「又黎18件麥樂雞！？」<br />\n<br />\n到最後，佢都要重新執一次個餐俾我，但最主要係引證到肥婆望到肉都係不能夠抵擋誘惑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎大家一齊狙擊肥婆！</span>"},{"pid":"e661d978ab7dcc70c12066fd5af200bb40164a51","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292fbcf621d7c62f98f26af700b361d4941dd2c1","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5c1d0e60fbe6ce7659d98b9cd4e464743bd948","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:25:46.000Z","msg":"邊個肥婆比負評！"},{"pid":"3da15add252ab443b2cf8a4f1657b1c766b5789c","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24d4c7bb4bf5a378826e9d5b151784cd20921e4","tid":200934,"uid":40796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:27:53.000Z","msg":"正常程序 應該係一手交單 一手交貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個肥婆點拎到？"},{"pid":"e26bb69935cdda819aac5b3ec1e12f105de48bb3","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常程序 應該係一手交單 一手交貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個肥婆點拎到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炮台山 職員六點會送餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢唔check單就放低比個客係錯。<br />\n但係唔係你既餐你就出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a1553499032e0da7c0cb739af11e86e818423a","tid":200934,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:34:02.000Z","msg":"首先"},{"pid":"1337338008c297621ccfc03562bdc4d4157aecaa","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T11:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先</blockquote><br />\n你要肥婆圖？"},{"pid":"c1b66b7112ff90b6918f5ea3d426adfbad8b6d2a","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T12:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2288d011c9bdd81bf4ab164f2aa59726214bc1b3","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"964ef4f98930b413509faf1a423d38c7a3bdfc9c","tid":200934,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}